    <item>
      <title>前莫桑比克部长因美国债券欺诈被判八年半监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ex-mozambique-minister-gets-8-1-2-years-in-us-bond-fraud-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克前财政部长因参与瑞士信贷集团 20 亿美元债券欺诈案被美国法官判处 8 年半监禁，该欺诈案引发了该非洲国家的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ex-mozambique-minister-gets-8-1-2-years-in-us-bond-fraud-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 19:36:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会称微软与 OpenAI 合作引发反垄断担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/microsoft-openai-partnership-raises-antitrust-concerns-ftc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦贸易委员会在周五发布的一份报告中表示，微软公司对 OpenAI 的 130 亿美元投资引发了人们的担忧，人们担心这家科技巨头可能会将其在云计算领域的主导地位延伸到新兴的人工智能市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/microsoft-openai-partnership-raises-antitrust-concerns-ftc</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 19:20:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院维持法律后，TikTok 的命运掌握在特朗普手中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/tiktok-s-future-hinges-on-trump-following-supreme-court-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院结束了 TikTok 长达九个月的法律纠纷，迫使该公司内部和北京的领导人考虑越来越少的替代方案，以让这款流行的视频分享应用继续存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/tiktok-s-future-hinges-on-trump-following-supreme-court-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 17:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市长亚当斯称与特朗普举行了“富有成效”的会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/new-york-mayor-adams-plans-pre-inauguration-meeting-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯表示，他周五与唐纳德·特朗普进行了“富有成效的谈话”，谈到了许多问题，包括以色列与哈马斯停火协议对公共安全的影响以及如何吸引制造业工作岗位到纽约市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/new-york-mayor-adams-plans-pre-inauguration-meeting-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国调查组寻求新逮捕令以延长尹某的拘捕期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/south-korean-president-yoon-remains-in-detention-for-time-being</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，韩国总统尹锡烈因发布不合时宜的戒严令而遭弹劾，韩国调查人员随后申请签发新的逮捕令，延长对他的拘留期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/south-korean-president-yoon-remains-in-detention-for-time-being</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 03:03:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
